NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Bugtracker - automatically sets the bugtracker URL

VERSION
    version 1.100700

SYNOPSIS
    In "dist.ini":

        [Bugtracker]

DESCRIPTION
    This is an extension of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::InlineFiles, providing the
    following files

      xt/release/synopsis.t - a standard Test::Synopsis test

FUNCTIONS
  metadata
    Sets the bugtracker URL in the distribution's metadata.

INSTALLATION
    See perlmodinstall for information and options on installing Perl
    modules.

